channel.title: Translate This [NWS!]
channel.description:
NWS means not work safe. That means if your at work/place where you can't look at whatever you want on the computer, stop reading. Now then, translate this:
I'm sure someone once advise you to never sell yourself short. It was probably the old coughing whore with whom you shared the street. Where were you when she told you this? Luckily for me, you already had your head burrowed in car and couldn't hear, since the John was clutching your head around his dick...
